{"tid":418784,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【取消黃金周航班】海航為HK Express大股東","createTime":"2017-09-30T00:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T16:54:50.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7ae596f6cb90509c5821bed8519b0dbe0dd5cb","tid":418784,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506695628_56dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506695628_56dd.jpg&h=05c94765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHK Express（香港快運航空）突然取消大量黃金周航班，令大批遊客受影響。成立於2004年的HK Express前身為港聯航空，當時大股東賭王何鴻燊個人名義擁有香港快運航空55%股權，但經營一直虧損，直至2006年中資海航集團向何鴻燊購入當時港聯45%股權，並易名為香港快運。在海航入股後，於2013年正式轉型為廉航，亦是香港現時唯一的本地廉航公司。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，海航集團旗下海南航空於2006年收購原名中富航空主要股權，並易名香港航空。快運的「姊妹公司」，同為海航系的香港航空為傳統航空公司，主攻亞洲市場，但亦積極開拓長途航線，包括美國芝加哥﹑新西蘭﹑澳洲﹑俄羅斯等。<br />\n<br />\n海航集團是內地超級巨型企業，去年收入逾6,000億元人民幣，旗下有8間A股及3間香港上市公司。海航近年頻頻在海外大手投資，豪擲千億進行全球收購，包括在香港以約272億港元天價買下4幅啟德地皮。流亡海外的中國富豪郭文貴早前爆料，中紀委書記王岐山家族在海航集團有利益，令海航捲入政治風波。市場不斷傳出有外資銀行暫停融資消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57272903&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57272903%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170929&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72DmMrrXVyJ09QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=38970039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57272903%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170929&h=f6278fb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57272903&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170929</a>"},{"pid":"233623664304e5d6cfc4a4e6387e46f9b6df534c","tid":418784,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:58:14.000Z","msg":"【導師被離職 ?】HK Express取消航班　原因可能係...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506694831_e121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506694831_e121.jpg&h=daa4261c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506694933_000f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506694933_000f.jpg&h=943d80be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港快運（HK Express）突然取消黃金周18班航班，估計受影響乘客多達3,000名乘客，然而出事前Facebook已傳出香港快運因培訓隊伍離職，10月可能有150名機組人員未能工作！<br />\n<br />\n本月中Facebook群組「HK Express苦主關注組」有疑似前職員留言，預告「如果幾星期後發覺你們的航班開始被取消，請不要太驚訝」。留言稱，由於三名安全部門導師被迫離職，而新請的導師尚未從民航處取得導師執照，故所有新班暫停培訓。<br />\n<br />\n然而，空中服務員每年必須重新上一次安全培訓，才可繼續工作，該職員估計10月或有150名空中服務員和機師因未上安全培訓而不能工作，佔總數約25%。留言續指，公司未知新導師何時能取得牌照，情況可能惡化。其後香港快運曾證實確出現相關問題，聲稱已解決，而民航處早前亦收到報告，當時公司稱航班運作暫時不受影響。言猶在耳，香港快運今日已出事，未知是否因上述原因所致。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報今晚向HK Express查詢取消航班是否與導師及安全培訓有關，公司未肯作出回應，只重申「對於十月上旬部份航班更改影響旅客原定行程，HK Express深感抱歉，已即時採取積極措施，並竭盡所能作出補救。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57272873&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57272873%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170929&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72DmMrrXVyJ09QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c11862bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57272873%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170929&h=f9611eae\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57272873&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170929</a>"},{"pid":"63444ee9177505a63777e31edf6d85660458c2e4","tid":418784,"uid":13724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:10:55.000Z","msg":"被離職乜鬼吖，三條友跟上司走㗎，個上司自己有好路數玩嘢"},{"pid":"4ecab1687ec82fb40a364594843094f00f2886f4","tid":418784,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【導師被離職 ?】HK Express取消航班　原因可能係...<br />\n<br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506694831_e121.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506694831_e121.jpg%22&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72DmMrrXVyJ09QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0dfe1d58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506694831_e121.jpg&quot;</a>  /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506694933_000f.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506694933_000f.jpg%22&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72DmMrrXVyJ09QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3badb920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506694933_000f.jpg&quot;</a>  /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n香港快運（HK Express）突然取消黃金周18班航班，估計受影響乘客多達3,000名乘客，然而出事前Facebook已傳出香港快運因培訓隊伍離職，10月可能有150名機組人員未能工作！<br />\n<br />\n本月中Facebook群組「HK Express苦主關注組」有疑似前職員留言，預告「如果幾星期後發覺你們的航班開始被取消，請不要太驚訝」。留言稱，由於三名安全部門導師被迫離職，而新請的導師尚未從民航處取得導師執照，故所有新班暫停培訓。<br />\n<br />\n然而，空中服務員每年必須重新上一次安全培訓，才可繼續工作，該職員估計10月或有150名空中服務員和機師因未上安全培訓而不能工作，佔總數約25%。留言續指，公司未知新導師何時能取得牌照，情況可能惡化。其後香港快運曾證實確出現相關問題，聲稱已解決，而民航處早前亦收到報告，當時公司稱航班運作暫時不受影響。言猶在耳，香港快運今日已出事，未知是否因上述原因所致。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報今晚向HK Express查詢取消航班是否與導師及安全培訓有關，公司未肯作出回應，只重申「對於十月上旬部份航班更改影響旅客原定行程，HK Express深感抱歉，已即時採取積極措施，並竭盡所能作出補救。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57272873&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57272873%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170929&d=%2FzwbaqiJ72DmMrrXVyJ09QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c11862bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57272873%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170929&h=f9611eae\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57272873&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170929</a></blockquote><br />\n抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250d6590fd24503ca239b3b2e448085ea498a942","tid":418784,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:14:59.000Z","msg":"嗰班坐hk express嘅鬼殺咁嘈，坐得廉航預咗失預算，費用之一，平嘢就係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6221fa551aca753c992cd27464000d699d3594","tid":418784,"uid":47986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"大陸野信唔過就不嬲<br />\n最不值係HX, UO打香港旗號<br />\n很香港？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01063cf12a7c3ed568ed2d59409cc88009eca16d","tid":418784,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰班坐hk express嘅鬼殺咁嘈，坐得廉航預咗失預算，費用之一，平嘢就係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不能同意更多，所以我從來唔坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c540cbbd6e1fb6adf885d986ab1c57443d916f","tid":418784,"uid":30841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸野信唔過就不嬲<br />\n最不值係HX, UO打香港旗號<br />\n很香港？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有間687香港國際建設投資。。。個名水蛇春咁長<br />\n明明唔係港企扁扁要加個香港係前面"},{"pi